  "text": "so that the flat plateau phase should be present for q \u2248 1/\u03b3, i.e. close to q = 8/3 in the uniform medium and q = 4 in the wind case. In the presented example [CITATION_1] considered the temporal decay index after the plateau \u03b1 2 = \u22121.5, leading to q = 1/(2\u03b3) and the parameters of the central engine energy deposition in the late afterglow stage q = 4/3 and 2, for the uniform medium and the wind case, respectively. It should be noted that this example uses the \u03b1 2 value very close to the mean value of our distribution, \u03b1 mean = 1.4 \u00b1 0.3, as visible in the upper panel of Fig. 1 .",
